# GloveCubs Operations Truth

- Inventory mutations must be atomic (reserve, release, deduct).
- Available quantity must reflect real inventory minus reservations.
- Discounts must not bypass pricing floors or margin constraints.
- Margin protection rules override promotional logic.
- Shipping charges shown to users must match persisted order values.
- Do not replace persisted shipping or discount values with recalculated estimates.
- Operational state (inventory, shipping, discounts) must always be derived from trusted persisted data.---
alwaysApply: true
